  (async () => {
    const response = await fetch("/api/data");
    const result = await response.json();
    setData(result);
  })();
}, []);
```

вЬЕ Works  
вЪ†пЄП Slightly less readable  
вЬЕ Often seen in seniorвАСlevel codebases

